@baseUrl = http://host.docker.internal:8000

### Status service
Get {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Create company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "legal_number": "20600000001",
    "legal_name": "Mi Empresa S.A.C.",
    "trade_name": "Mi Empresa",
    "sunat_mode": "demo",
    "soap_send_type": "sunat",
    "soap_username": "MODDATOS",
    "soap_password": "",
    "certificate_b64": ""
}

### Get company
Get {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/companies/20600000001
Content-Type: application/json
